  <name>MultiWall</name>
  <summary>Multi-Monitor Wallpaper Manager</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      MultiWall is a GTK4 application that allows you to set different wallpapers
      for each monitor in a multi-monitor setup. It supports various display modes
      (fill, fit, stretch, center, tile) and provides a real-time preview of your
      wallpaper configuration.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Individual wallpaper configuration for each monitor</li>
      <li>Multiple display modes (fill, fit, stretch, center, tile)</li>
      <li>Real-time preview of wallpaper layout</li>
      <li>Custom background colors</li>
      <li>Auto-save configuration</li>
      <li>Multi-language support (English, Spanish)</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  
